    <item>
      <title>白宫表示将于周六开始征收关税，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/dollar-falls-on-report-that-us-tariffs-delayed-until-march-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，美国关税将于周六按计划开始，美元随即上涨，加剧了当天的波动，有关特朗普总统标志性政策之一的报道导致各大货币大幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/dollar-falls-on-report-that-us-tariffs-delayed-until-march-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 17:47:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普关税临近，世界各国准备应对股市溢出效应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/as-trump-tariffs-near-world-braces-for-stock-market-spillover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普计划于周六对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收关税。现在的问题是，这将如何影响全球股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/as-trump-tariffs-near-world-braces-for-stock-market-spillover</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 17:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
